<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <title>Order Confirmation</title>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />
        <style>
            body {
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
                background-color: #f4f4f4;
            }

            .container {
                max-width: 600px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
                min-height: 100vh;
                background-color: #4f5ef1;
                color: #ffffff;
                box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            .message-sm {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 18px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                padding-top: 50px;
            }

            .message-sm > h1 {
                font-size: 25px;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .course-info {
                margin: auto;
                padding: 20px;
                width: 100%;
                background-color: #fff;
                border-radius: 10px;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
                box-shadow: 2px 2px 2px 2px rgba(206, 197, 197, 0.1);
                color: #000;
                box-sizing: border-box;
            }

            .course-info > h4 {
                color: #23bd70;
                font-size: 22px;
                font-weight: 500;
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 0;
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            table {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                table-layout: fixed;
            }

            td {
                padding: 10px;
                text-align: left;
            }

            .price-table {
                text-align: right;
            }

            .price-table td {
                text-align: right;
                padding-right: 0;
            }

            .footer {
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 50px;
                padding: 20px;
                color: #ffffff;
                font-size: 14px;
            }

            .footer a {
                text-decoration: none;
                color: #ffffff;
            }
            .table-equal {
                width: 100%;
                border-collapse: collapse;
                table-layout: fixed;
            }

            .table-equal th,
            .table-equal td {
                text-align: center;
                vertical-align: middle;
                padding: 10px;
                word-wrap: break-word;
            }

            .table-equal thead th {
                text-transform: uppercase;
                color: #0000006c;
                font-size: 16px;
                font-weight: 600;
            }

            .table-equal tbody td {
                font-weight: 500;
                color: #000000af;
                font-size: 15px;
            }

            @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
                .container {
                    padding: 10px;
                }
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="message-sm">
                <h1>Your ELearning order is confirmed!</h1>
                <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="course-info">
                <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>

                <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f">
                    <tr>
                        <td>Order #: <%= order._id %></td>
                        <td style="text-align: right">Order Date: <%= order.date %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>

                <table class="table-equal" style="margin-top: 10px">
                    <colgroup>
                        <col />
                        <col />
                        <col />
                    </colgroup>
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>ITEM</th>
                            <th>QTY</th>
                            <th>COST</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td><%= order.name %></td>
                            <td>1</td>
                            <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>

                <table style="width: 100%; border-top: 1px solid #00000029; margin-top: 20px">
                    <tr>
                        <td style="text-align: left">Subtotal:</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right">$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td style="text-align: left">Total:</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right">$<%= order.price %></td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>
                    If you have any questions, please contact our support team at
                    <a href="mailto:support@ELearning.com">support@ELearning.com</a>
                </p>
                <p>&copy; 2025 ELearning. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
